title: UWS' Botten, Nelson Earn All-UMAC Honor
text:
UWS' Botten, Nelson Earn All-UMAC Honor 
By Zach Schneider UWS' Botten, Nelson Earn All-UMAC Honor October 12, 2015 Updated Oct 12, 2015 at 3:57 PM CDT 
Superior, WI (NNCNOW.com) --- UW-Superior freshmen golfers Hayley Botten and Allie Nelson have both been named to the all-Upper Midwest Athletic Conference (UMAC) team, it was announced on Monday afternoon. 
Botten and Nelson were the Yellowjackets' top scorers this past weekend at the UMAC championships, with UW-Superior winning that tournament by 15 strokes.
